INFOCONSENT_HEADER: Dadka la wadaag in lagaa helay fayrusta
INFOCONSENT_DESCRIPTION: Waxaad dooratay inaad dadka kale u sheegto in lagaa helay covid-19. Dadka loo dirayo ogeysiisku ma ogaan karaan in adigu tahay qofka laga helay fayrusta.
INFOCONSENT_LOOKUP_TEXT: Markaad Smittestopp ku dirayso ogeysiin ku saabsan in lagaa helay covid-19, waxa Smittestopp marka hore eegayaa in qaadistaada laga diiwaangeliyey Nidaamka Ogeysiinta cudurrada la kala qaado (MSIS) oo Machadka Caafimaadka Dadweynuhu masuul ka yahay. Lambarkaaga dhalashada ayaa la isticmaalayaa si loo hubiyo in la diiwaangeliyey in fayrus lagaa helay. Taas darteed waa inaad ku gasho ID-porten.
INFOCONSENT_NOTIFICATION_TEXT: Haddii ka hubinta MSIS xaqiijiso in la diiwaangeliyey in tijaabadii lagaa qaaday laga helay covid-19, waxa Smittestopp markaa telefoonnada kale ee wata barmaamijyada raad-raaca faafitaanka oo daaran u fasaxayaa xogtii la isticmaalay markii la samaynayey furayaasha u dhawaanshaha. Xogtaasi waa waa furayaal hal dhinac u socda oo aan lagugu garan karin, laakiin ay telefoonnada kale ku ogaan karaan inay u dhawaayeen telefoonkaaga. Haddii la ogaado in telefoono kale u dhawaayeen telefoonkaaga, waxa dadka isticmaalaya telefoonadaas heli doonaan ogeysiin loogu dirayo telefoonkooda. Waxa iyaga la siin doonaa talo ku saabsan waxay samayn karaan. Smittestopp waxa loo sameeyey qaab aan cid kale ku ogaan karin qofka soo sheegay in laga helay fayrusta. Haddii qofka helay ogeysiintu aanu dad badan u dhawaanin wakhtiyadii dambe, waxa qofkaasi garan karaa qofka soo gudbiyey ogeysiinta.
INFOCONSENT_CONSENT_BEAWARE_TEXT: Markaad oggolaato in la diro ogeysiin, oo ogeysiintiina la diray, ma ka laaban kartid oggolaanshaha.
INFOCONSENT_CONSENT_EXPLANATION_TEXT: Waan oggolahay in dadka aan u dhawaaday loo diro ogeysiin ku saabsan in qof ay u dhawaadeen laga helay covid-19.  Si loo diri karo ogeysiinta, waxaan oggolahay in la eego Nidaamka Ogeysiinta ee cudurrada la is qaadsiiyo (MSIS). Sidaas ayaa Machadka Caafimaadka Dadweynuhu ku hubsan karaa in fayrusta la iga helay ka hor intaan ogeysiin loo dirin dad kale. Dadka hela ogeysiintu ma ogaan karaan in anigu soo sheegay in la iga helay fayrusta.
